cdata.name: Centra
cdata.desc:
Centra Tech has designed amulti-blockchain debit card that connects to a smart wallet that is safe, secure, and more importantly insured. Centracurrentlysupports 8+ major cryptocurrencies: Bitcoin, Ethereum, ERC20 Tokens, Litecoin, Ripple, Dash, Zcash, &Monerowith more to come. Centra team designed a platform to create a global account solution for anyone wholackbanking resources.

Centra Tech is also launching a platform called Coin Bay (www.cBay.io) which will be the world's first Amazon style store that is designed to be cryptocurrency acceptable.
